<span id="Description"></span>
== Descripción ==

La herramienta [[Image:Sketcher_ViewSketch.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_ViewSketch|Croquizador Vista Croquis]] alinea la [[3D_View|Vista 3D]] con el croquis. La vista se rota de forma que su dirección sea perpendicular al plano del boceto, y el eje X del boceto aparece horizontal. Resulta útil si ha cambiado la orientación de la vista para examinar otro aspecto del modelo y desea volver a la vista de boceto predeterminada.

<span id="Usage"></span>
== Uso ==

See also: [[Sketcher_Preferences#Display|Sketcher Preferences]].

# This tool is only available if a sketch is in [[Sketcher_EditSketch|edit mode]].
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Sketcher_ViewSketch.svg|16px]] [[Sketcher_ViewSketch|Align View to Sketch]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Sketch → [[Image:Sketcher_ViewSketch.svg|16px]] Align View to Sketch}} option from the menu.
#* Right-click in the [[3D_View|3D View]] and select the {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Sketcher_ViewSketch.svg|16px]] Align View to Sketch}} option from the context menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|Q}} then {{KEY|P}}.


